Class AddressBookSystemTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • systemtests.AddressBookSystemTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddCommandSystemTest, ClearCommandSystemTest, DeleteCommandSystemTest, EditCommandSystemTest, ErrorDialogGuiTest, FindCommandSystemTest, HelpCommandSystemTest, SampleDataTest, SelectCommandSystemTest 

    public abstract class AddressBookSystemTest
extends java.lang.Object
    A system test class for AddressBook, which provides access to handles of GUI components and helper methods for test verification.
